content: No file will be copied. The original file will be retained in the destination folder.

comment.text: This translation key provides a message to be displayed when skipping file copy operations, indicating that the original file will remain in the destination folder. It appears in UI elements where users can choose to skip copying files, such as a conflict resolution dialog.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Heç bir fayl köçürülmədi. Orijinal fayl köçürülən yerdə dəyişikliksiz qaldı.' isn't a direct or optimal translation of 'No file will be copied. The original file will be retained in the destination folder.'. 'Köçürülən yerdə dəyişikliksiz qaldı' implies the original file remained unchanged *at the copied location*, which is not the intended meaning.  The phrase 'destination folder' specifically refers to the place the file *wasn't* copied *to*.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Heç bir fayl surüşdürülmədi. Orijinal fayl, məqsədli qovluqda saxlanıldı.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: There is an unnecessary space before the colon after "չի պատճենվի".
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Ոչ մի ֆայլ չի պատճենվի։Բնօրինակ ֆայլը կպահվի նպատակակետի պանակում

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ໄຟລ໌' (file) is repeated excessively. While technically correct, it sounds unnatural in Lao.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນໂຟນເດີ້, ແບບບໍ່ມີການສຳເນົາ.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'ໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນໂຟນເດີ້' could be slightly improved for flow. The 'ຈະຖືກ' construct can sometimes be softened depending on the desired nuance.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບຈະເກັບໄວ້ໃນໂຟນເດີ້.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Latvian translation 'Fails tiks pievienots failam ar tādu pašu nosaukumu kā versijai.' does not accurately reflect the English meaning 'No file will be copied. The original file will be retained in the destination folder.' It translates to something like 'A file will be added to a file with the same name as a version.' This is incorrect as the English text describes a skipped copy, not a version creation.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: The correct translation should convey that the file is not copied and the original is kept. For example: 'Fails netiks kopēts. Oriģinālais fails tiks paturēts galamērķa mapē.'

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'Niciun fișier n-o să fie copiat' is grammatically correct but sounds slightly awkward in modern Romanian. The contraction 'n-' is a bit archaic in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Niciun fișier nu va fi copiat.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'dosarul de destinație' is slightly formal. Depending on the target audience and tone of the application, a less formal option might be preferred.
The word 'фолдеру' is a less common and potentially less professional term. 'Фолдеру' is a more accurate transliteration and commonly used.
